      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下：thanksSigningUp同时指向thanksVerifying和pendingConfirmation，然后thanksVerifying指向pendingApproval。另外pendingConfirmation和thanksVerifying之间有关系吗？",
